title: Oath
author: ShikamaruNara
pages:
#- I, in the presence of almighty heaven, do solemnly swear, that I will henceforth faithfully support, protect, and defend the Heavenly Kingdom of Gensokyo, and the Confederation of the States thereunder; and that I will, in like manner, abide by, and
#- faithfully support all laws and proclamations which have been made in her name, so help me God. This Oath is taken and accepted, with the full understanding that if the party receiving it be found hereafter in arms against the government of Gensokyo
#- or aiding and abetting its enemies, the penalty will be indefinite imprisonment or otherwise in accordance with the law.§0
§0
§0~ShikamaruNara
#- 